room_title: Escape room "Ava Flambeaux's House of Voodoo" by The Room - Wichita in Wichita
room_description:
You are in the inner sanctum of Ava Flambeaux’s House of Voodoo. Miss Ava Flambeaux is one of America’s oldest practicing Voodoo Queens. Miss Flambeaux has placed a curse on one of your beloved family members through a Voodoo Doll that’s locked away in her safe.
You have one hour to decipher the clues, swap the doll and exit the room before Ava returns and places a curse on you!
